<bibRefCitation author="Pallas, P. S." box="[1213,1432,1650,1676]" pageId="1" pageNumber="21" refId="ref2728" refString="Pallas, P. S. (1803) Illustrationes plantarum imperfecte vel nondum cognitarum, cum centuria iconum. Academico Petropolitano, Leipzig, 129 pp." type="book" year="1803">Pallas (1803: 52)</bibRefCitation>
